description: This file defines a React functional component for a Jira Projects page. It provides UI elements for searching and creating Jira projects via an API, managing state for user inputs, loading states, and displaying results or errors.

methods.name: search
methods.description: Asynchronously invokes the 'search_projects' Jira tool with provided tenant and connector IDs along with a search query, then updates the result state or error state based on the response.

methods.name: create
methods.description: Asynchronously invokes the 'create_project' Jira tool with provided tenant and connector IDs, using the query as the project name, then updates the result or error state accordingly.
